  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check out our next game!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Practise your sidestep skills as you dodge spells coming at you from all directions. Slay minions and level up to choose from a variety of upgrades and new abilities to increase your chances of survival. Explore different skill combinations and unlock combo upgrades to create powerful synergies.<br><br><br><br>Vampire Survivors meets League of Legends in this moba inspired action rogue lite.<br><br>Sidestep or use your abilities to dodge the storm of abilities thrown at you<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create synergies with combo upgrades<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/f97773e1a251f2da2b49ff458b338c05.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kill the minions before they become too many to handle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And watch out for the boss<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick 20-ish minutes rounds<br></li><li>8 playable characters each with their own unique starting passive ability<br></li><li>Large pool of active abilities and passive upgrades to choose from during gameplay<br></li><li>Many combo upgrades that unlock when certain combinations of abilities has been chosen that adds new synergetic functionality to the abilities<br></li><li>Skill tree with permanent upgrades that makes you stronger after each run<br></li><li>4 maps with increasing difficulty<br></li><li>Curse upgrade system in the skill tree to increase the difficulty to crazy levels<br></li><li>3 different types of leaderboards for each map</li></ul><br>If you like more active horde survival games like Soulstone Survivors and 20 Minutes Till Dawn I think you will enjoy this as well.",
  "about_the_game": "Practise your sidestep skills as you dodge spells coming at you from all directions. Slay minions and level up to choose from a variety of upgrades and new abilities to increase your chances of survival. Explore different skill combinations and unlock combo upgrades to create powerful synergies.<br><br><br><br>Vampire Survivors meets League of Legends in this moba inspired action rogue lite.<br><br>Sidestep or use your abilities to dodge the storm of abilities thrown at you<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/611c3323a582b6cf2407368f38e10191.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create synergies with combo upgrades<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/f97773e1a251f2da2b49ff458b338c05.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/c43e0aab6a4c995402d2d9c14f11e027.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kill the minions before they become too many to handle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/b9cd98383da67689f9b4e2a92fd031ec.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And watch out for the boss<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.poster.avif?t=1695375905\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.webm?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077590/extras/a6bbc79fd0fd628cde4c50060e1976d8.mp4?t=1695375905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick 20-ish minutes rounds<br></li><li>8 playable characters each with their own unique starting passive ability<br></li><li>Large pool of active abilities and passive upgrades to choose from during gameplay<br></li><li>Many combo upgrades that unlock when certain combinations of abilities has been chosen that adds new synergetic functionality to the abilities<br></li><li>Skill tree with permanent upgrades that makes you stronger after each run<br></li><li>4 maps with increasing difficulty<br></li><li>Curse upgrade system in the skill tree to increase the difficulty to crazy levels<br></li><li>3 different types of leaderboards for each map</li></ul><br>If you like more active horde survival games like Soulstone Survivors and 20 Minutes Till Dawn I think you will enjoy this as well.",
